    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with the MRL 2 assessment plan. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission. Note: this package was submitted under the Minimal profile; the intended-use scope was communicated informally through the assessment narrative rather than through a structured ContextOfUse record.",
